description:
Machine washable and perfect for littles who aren’t quite ready for the bench seat, the Second Seat for the Joovy Qool stroller holds kids up to 55 lbs.

-4 reclining positions

-Can be placed in the high, middle, or low positions

-Five-point adjustable harness

-Compatible with Joovy Qool stroller

-Holds up to 55 lbs

When your big kid still isn't quite big enough for the bench seat, the second seat is a must-have. With an easy recline, five-point harness, and plenty of cushion, the Second Seat is great when you need it and easy to remove when you don’t.
name: Joovy 1EACH
